API_ROUTES

GET /games                            : List all games
GET /games/{id}                       : Returns info of a game
GET /games/{game_id}/challenges       : Returns the challenges of a certain game
GET /challenges/                      : List all challenges of all games
GET /challenges/{challenge_id}        : Returns all the infos along with the scores of a certain challenge

POST /games                           : Creates a game
POST /games/{game_id}/challenges      : Creates a challenge

PUT /games/{id}                       : Edit a certain game
PUT /challenges/{challenge_id}        : Edit a certain challenge


DELETE /games/{id}                       : Deletes a certain game
DELETE /challenges/{challenge_id}        : Deletes a certain challenge

POST /challenges/{challenge_id}/complete : Completes a certain challenge one time
POST /challenges/{challenge_id}/cancel   : Cancels the success of a certain challenge one time




